---
import Layout from '../../../../../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const breadcrumbs = [
  { text: 'Recruiting Team', href: '/docs/team/recruiting' },
  { text: 'Job Descriptions', href: '/docs/team/recruiting/job-descriptions-jds' },
  { text: 'Copywriter', href: '/docs/team/recruiting/job-descriptions-jds/copywriter' }
];

---

<Layout title="Lead Copywriter">
  <main class="py-8 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <article class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto">
      <nav class="flex mb-2" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <ol class="flex items-center">
          {breadcrumbs.map((crumb, index) => (
            <li class="flex items-center">
              {index > 0 && <span class="mx-2 text-gray-400">/</span>}
              <a href={crumb.href} class="text-sm text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900">
                {crumb.text}
              </a>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ol>
      </nav>

      <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
        <h1>Lead Copywriter</h1>

        <h2>About [Company Name]</h2>
        <p>Add a bit about your company here.</p>

        <h2>Role Overview</h2>
        <p>As a Lead Copywriter at [Company Name], you will play a pivotal role in crafting compelling and impactful content that aligns with our brand voice and enhances user engagement. This position requires a seasoned professional who can lead content initiatives, collaborate with cross-functional teams, and mentor junior writers.</p>

        <h2>What You'll Do</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Lead the development and execution of high-quality content for web, mobile, and other digital platforms.</li>
          <li>Collaborate with engineers, designers, and marketing teams to create cohesive and engaging user experiences.</li>
          <li>Help conduct thorough research to inform and support content development.</li>
          <li>Ensure all content aligns with [Company]'s brand voice and style guidelines.</li>
          <li>Mentor junior writers and provide constructive feedback to elevate the overall quality of content.</li>
          <li>Analyze content performance and make data-driven decisions to optimize engagement.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>What We're Looking For</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Bachelor's degree in English, Communications, Journalism, or a related field, or equivalent practical experience.</li>
          <li>7-12 years of experience in content writing with a strong portfolio showcasing your work.</li>
          <li>Expertise in content strategy and digital content creation.</li>
          <li>Excellent communication and presentation skills.</li>
          <li>Ability to manage multiple projects and work collaboratively in a team environment.</li>
          <li>Strong leadership and mentoring skills.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Why Join [Company Name]</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Be part of a rapidly growing company that's shaping the future of how people connect online.</li>
          <li>Contribute to a product that impacts millions of users worldwide, driving innovation in digital experiences.</li>
          <li>Enjoy a collaborative, inclusive, and creative work environment that values diversity and fosters professional growth.</li>
          <li>Benefit from a competitive compensation package, flexible work arrangements, and a commitment to work-life balance.</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">[Company Name] is committed to providing a competitive compensation package. Our cash compensation amount for this role is targeted at $X-$X in X area. Final offer amounts are determined by multiple factors, including candidate expertise, the scope of role and level, and may vary from the amounts listed above.</p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>
